<L>__{interior mark's office evening}
<A>__{as haven finishes his statement. he is again at the window, glancing out. perhaps he has seen the incident with mick and jerry across the crowded street.}
<C>__{haven}
<D>__{...after i left there, i opened the crate. the gold was in it.}
<A>__{he turns back into the room. mark is looking at him with puzzled wonder, his face drawn and tense.}
<C>__{haven}
<D>__{that's all.}
<A>__{he smiles slightly. the wonder leaves mark's face. urbane cunning replaces it.}
<C>__{bristow}
<D>__{not quite.}
